# Production Environment Variables for VH Beyond the Horizons Website
# Copy this to your Vercel dashboard environment variables

# NextAuth Configuration (Required for Google OAuth)
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret_here
NEXTAUTH_URL=https://vh-beyondthehorizons.vercel.app
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your_nextauth_secret_here

# MongoDB Configuration (Required for Mental Math leaderboards)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/vh-website?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# EmailJS Configuration (Required for contact form)
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_emailjs_service_id_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_emailjs_template_id_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_emailjs_public_key_here

# Resend Configuration (Required for registration email notifications)
# Sign up at https://resend.com/ and get your API key
# Sends emails to: ahnaf816@gmail.com, hasanxsarower@gmail.com, ahnafahad16@gmail.com
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

# Instructions for setup:
#
# EmailJS Setup:
# 1. Go to https://www.emailjs.com/ and create an account
# 2. Create a new service (Gmail, Outlook, etc.)
# 3. Create an email template with the following variables:
#    - {{to_email}} - Recipient email (ahnafahad@vh-beyondthehorizons.org)
#    - {{from_name}} - Student's name
#    - {{from_email}} - Student's email
#    - {{subject}} - Email subject
#    - {{message}} - Form data message
# 4. Copy the Service ID, Template ID, and Public Key to the variables above
# 5. Set these variables in your Vercel deployment dashboard
#
# Resend Setup (for registration notifications):
# 1. Go to https://resend.com/ and create an account (free tier: 100 emails/day)
# 2. Get your API key from the dashboard
# 3. (Optional) Add and verify your domain for branded emails
#    - Without a verified domain, emails will be sent from onboarding@resend.dev
#    - With a verified domain, you can use your own email address
# 4. Copy the API key to RESEND_API_KEY variable above
# 5. Add this variable to your Vercel deployment dashboard